{"tid":1653582,"cid":12,"subCid":0,"title":"發夢見到家人係警, 鄰居係警, 叔伯大媽, 街頭街尾都係","createTime":"2019-10-14T06:53:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-27T08:34:44.000Z","uid":236799,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"95d76ff457d784f3b934462e53462ebef1d08192","tid":1653582,"uid":236799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T06:53:41.000Z","msg":"一起身見到個個都話自己係警。<br />\n底橫踢拖食緊煙又話係,<br />\n公園細路拎支膠棒fingfing吓又話係,<br />\n戴個超人面具又話係,<br />\n幾個揹住背囊又話係,<br />\n買緊餸又話係。<br />\n<br />\n見到有人打交,<br />\n一個就「你襲警呀拿!」, 一個又「放低手上武器!」。<br />\n「你張趴屎呢!」「唔需要比你睇! 你都冇冧把!」<br />\n自己望望吓就拾吓拾吓衝入去嗌埋一份,「係咪阻差辦公呀!」<br />\n<br />\n突然畀人兜巴星, 一開眼望見自己房個天花板。<br />\n原來係老母入左黎, 「醒未呀你, 幾點呀家陣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />」<br />\n「你又係警?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />」<br />\n「係呀景呀, 夠哂鐘去翠景攞位呀! 訓慒咗你呀!<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />」<br />\n<br />\n屌, 發夢啫<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wfc2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"170e0459644824d02df91ac06a9b46be224f444c","tid":1653582,"uid":29153,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T06:59:44.000Z","msg":"希望炒車"},{"pid":"53573dc2ad201317e4856edacf75ffa3ccd4048c","tid":1653582,"uid":61748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T07:01:47.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b9c548b28309bdfcf73dbccb83637d44caa56f23","tid":1653582,"uid":147017,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T07:05:21.000Z","msg":"啟示錄"},{"pid":"19825dedd83f7b0c3cbf1aefd9646c58c52511ef","tid":1653582,"uid":16613,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T07:05:22.000Z","msg":"大家明唔明樓主想講咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5503ea84a3fcd0d99e8faf1befc93c695dbdc792","tid":1653582,"uid":236799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T07:15:03.000Z","msg":"冇